{
  "stem": "4113.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This cousin who was in the Polish army was shipped off and joined the Polish army when Stalin allowed the Polish government in exile to form an army and take them to the Middle East-- via the Middle East, and to fight on the Allied side.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's how they were taken away, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so they all wanted to come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Soviets packed them off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as they came back, they told of the atrocities, the Sonderkommandos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For example, my cousin-- we had relatives in Stanislawow, which was a large city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Something like, I believe close to 10,000 Jews were shot by these Sonderkommandos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We heard all that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But this did not occur where we were at.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So many of these people came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And life went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we heard of all the atrocities that were going-- that was going on in the east.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then came 1941, December, 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I remember it was around Hanukkah time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, the Germans [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] got stuck in the Soviet winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Initially, of course, they marched forward very rapidly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Considering the roads in the Soviet Union, which were mud roads, you know, they rapidly moved eastward, very rapidly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Within weeks they're already near Smolensk, near Leningrad, Kiev, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All of a sudden comes the winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now they weren't prepared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hitler probably assumed that he will get the Ukrainians on this side, and by winter it will be over with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now the order came-- and I remember that evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Judenrat was called to come up to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stood at the window and watched them go up there, because the Gestapo was across the street from us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father went up.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
